# Animals

Animals are the heart of the zoo and the primary metric the player is trying to maximize. Each animal is a living entity with species-specific needs, moods, and breeding mechanics. The game includes 10 purchasable species across 5 biome types. See `animals/species_table.md` for the complete species data reference.

